Description:
Ballistics of the 105x607mm WB134P HEAT-FS fired from the Type 75 105mm recoilless rifle. The Type 75 is a copy of the M40A1 recoilless rifle with some modification. Projectile is stabilized with 6 fins deployed via central piston. Penetrates 150mm/65°. Drag in relation to 1943 drag curve i_43 = 1.545.

Projectile weighs 7.96 kg, loads 3.4 kg of 9/14 rosette high-nitrogen potassium. Web 0.8-1.0 mm, perforation diameter 0.35-0.55 mm, average length 10.0-13.0 mm according to 火炸药手册. Develops 650 kgf/cm^2 breech pressure and 503 m/s. Projectile travels 26.83dm, barrel measures 0.8849 dm^2 in cross section, chamber volume is 7.2 L and measures 4.9 dm in length, cross section 3.66 dm^2 at the breech. Throat area of 0.6677 dm^2. Projectile starts at 50 kgf/cm^2 per 火炮内弹道计算手册. 

Pressures are interpreted as copper crusher gauge values and converted accordingly.
